@startuml
title Sequence Diagram: Admin Evaluate Research

actor Admin
participant "Frontend/UI" as UI
participant "Backend/API" as API
participant "Auth Middleware (JWT)" as AUTH
database "Database (Neon)" as DB
participant "Notification Service (Optional)" as NOTI

Admin -> UI: Edit evaluation + Click Save
UI -> UI: Validate required fields
UI -> API: PATCH /trl/assessment/{id} (JWT + payload)

API -> AUTH: Verify JWT & role
AUTH --> API: Authorized / Forbidden

alt Forbidden
    API --> UI: 403 Forbidden
else Authorized
    API -> API: Validate payload schema
    alt Invalid Data
        API --> UI: 400 Validation Error
    else Valid
        API -> DB: Check assessment exists
        alt Not Found
            API --> UI: 404 Not Found
        else Exists
            API -> DB: BEGIN TRANSACTION
            API -> DB: Update evaluation fields
            API -> DB: Recalculate TRL Level
            API -> DB: Insert audit log
            DB --> API: Success
            API -> DB: COMMIT
            API -> NOTI: Send evaluation result (optional)
            NOTI --> API: Sent
            API --> UI: 200 Success
        end
    end
end

UI -> UI: Invalidate query cache
UI --> Admin: Show success toast

@enduml